     1→<!DOCTYPE html>
     2→<html lang="en">
     3→<head>
     4→<meta charset="UTF-8">
     5→<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
     6→<title>Habitat Residency — 7 days. 5 founders. One demo day.</title>
     7→<meta name="description" content="A 7-day live-in residency for founders who've already shipped. Dedicated space, mentorship, and a demo day with investors. Coming 2026.">
     8→<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
     9→<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    10→<style>
    11→:root {
    12→  --bg: #fafaf8;
    13→  --text: #1c1b1a;
    14→  --cream: #f0ede6;
    15→  --gray: #6b6864;
    16→  --gray-light: #8a8780;
    17→  --accent: #3d5afc;
    18→  --accent-glow: #2d4ae8;
    19→  --coral: #e85a35;
    20→  --teal: #16b889;
    21→  --purple: #7c4fcc;
    22→  --font-display: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    23→  --font-body: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    24→}
    25→
    26→*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    27→html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    28→body {
    29→  font-family: var(--font-body);
    30→  background: var(--bg);
    31→  color: var(--text);
    32→  line-height: 1.6;
    33→  overflow-x: hidden;
    34→  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    35→}
    36→a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    37→img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    38→
    39→.container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    40→section { padding: 120px 0; }
    41→
    42→/* NAV */
    43→nav {
    44→  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    45→  padding: 20px 0;
    46→  background: rgba(250,250,248,0.92);
    47→  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    48→  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(28,27,26,0.08);
    49→}
    50→nav .container { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    51→.logo { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    52→.logo span { color: var(--accent); }
    53→.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; align-items: center; list-style: none; }
    54→.nav-links a { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--gray); transition: color 0.2s; }
    55→.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    56→.nav-links a.active { color: var(--purple); font-weight: 500; }
    57→.nav-cta {
    58→  background: var(--accent); color: #ffffff !important;
    59→  padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 6px;
    60→  font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; transition: background 0.2s;
    61→}
    62→.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent-glow) !important; }
    63→
    64→/* HERO */
    65→.hero {
    66→  min-height: 80vh; display: flex; align-items: center;
    67→  padding-top: 100px; position: relative;
    68→}
    69→.hero::before {
    70→  content: ''; position: absolute; top: -100px; right: -200px;
    71→  width: 600px; height: 600px;
    72→  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,79,204,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
    73→  pointer-events: none;
    74→}
    75→.hero-label {
    76→  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 13px;
    77→  color: var(--purple); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    78→  margin-bottom: 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    79→}
    80→.hero-label::before { content: ''; width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--purple); }
    81→.coming-badge {
    82→  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    83→  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 11px;
    84→  letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    85→  background: rgba(124,79,204,0.1); color: var(--purple);
    86→  padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 24px;
    87→}
    88→.hero h1 {
    89→  font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 76px); font-weight: 700;
    90→  line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -2px; margin-bottom: 28px;
    91→}
    92→.hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--purple); }
    93→.hero-sub {
    94→  font-size: 20px; color: var(--gray); max-width: 580px;
    95→  line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 48px; font-weight: 300;
    96→}
    97→.hero-meta { display: flex; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    98→.hero-meta-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
    99→.hero-meta-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
   100→.hero-meta-value { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; }
   101→.hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
   102→
   103→.btn-primary {
   104→  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
   105→  background: var(--purple); color: #ffffff;
   106→  padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 8px;
   107→  font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;
   108→  transition: all 0.2s; border: none; cursor: pointer;
   109→}
   110→.btn-primary:hover { background: #6a3eb8; transform: translateY(-1px); }
   111→.btn-secondary {
   112→  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
   113→  background: transparent; color: var(--text);
   114→  padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 8px;
   115→  font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px;
   116→  border: 1px solid rgba(28,27,26,0.18); transition: all 0.2s; cursor: pointer;
   117→}
   118→.btn-secondary:hover { border-color: rgba(28,27,26,0.35); background: rgba(28,27,26,0.04); }
   119→
   120→/* SECTION ELEMENTS */
   121→.section-label {
   122→  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 13px;
   123→  color: var(--purple); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;
   124→}
   125→.section-title {
   126→  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px); font-weight: 700;
   127→  letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.1;
   128→}
   129→.section-sub { font-size: 18px; color: var(--gray); max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 64px; font-weight: 300; }
   130→
   131→/* WHAT IS IT */
   132→.intro-grid {
   133→  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px;
   134→  align-items: center; margin-top: 64px;
   135→}
   136→.intro-text h3 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
   137→.intro-text p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; }
   138→.intro-stats { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
   139→.intro-stat {
   140→  background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(28,27,26,0.08);
   141→  border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 28px;
   142→  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px;
   143→  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(28,27,26,0.04);
   144→}
   145→.intro-stat-num {
   146→  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 32px;
   147→  font-weight: 700; color: var(--purple); min-width: 80px;
   148→}
   149→.intro-stat-label { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.4; }
   150→
   151→/* WEEK SCHEDULE */
   152→.week-section { background: var(--cream); }
   153→.week-grid {
   154→  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
   155→  gap: 16px; margin-top: 64px;
   156→}
   157→.day-card {
   158→  background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(28,27,26,0.08);
   159→  border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px;
   160→  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(28,27,26,0.04);
   161→}
   162→.day-label {
   163→  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 11px;
   164→  letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
   165→  color: var(--purple); margin-bottom: 12px;
   166→}
   167→.day-card h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
   168→.day-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }
   169→
   170→/* MENTORSHIP */
   171→.mentorship-grid {
   172→  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
   173→  gap: 32px; margin-top: 64px;
   174→}
   175→.mentorship-card {
   176→  background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(28,27,26,0.08);
   177→  border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 32px;
   178→  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(28,27,26,0.04);
   179→  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
   180→}
   181→.mentorship-card::before {
   182→  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
   183→  background: var(--purple);
   184→}
   185→.mentorship-card h3 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; }
   186→.mentorship-card p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.7; }
   187→
   188→/* WHO IT'S FOR */
   189→.criteria-grid {
   190→  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
   191→  gap: 24px; margin-top: 64px;
   192→}
   193→.criteria-card {
   194→  background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(28,27,26,0.08);
   195→  border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px;
   196→  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(28,27,26,0.04);
   197→}
   198→.criteria-check {
   199→  width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
   200→  background: rgba(124,79,204,0.1); color: var(--purple);
   201→  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
   202→  font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px;
   203→}
   204→.criteria-card h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
   205→.criteria-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }
   206→
   207→/* NOT FOR */
   208→.not-for { background: var(--cream); }
   209→.not-for-list {
   210→  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
   211→  gap: 16px; margin-top: 40px;
   212→}
   213→.not-for-item {
   214→  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
   215→  background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(28,27,26,0.08);
   216→  border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px;
   217→}
   218→.not-for-x { color: var(--coral); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2px; }
   219→.not-for-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.5; }
   220→
   221→/* DEMO DAY */
   222→.demo-day-content {
   223→  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
   224→  gap: 80px; align-items: start; margin-top: 64px;
   225→}
   226→.demo-day-left p { font-size: 17px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; }
   227→.demo-day-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
   228→.demo-day-feature {
   229→  display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;
   230→}
   231→.demo-day-feature-dot {
   232→  width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%;
   233→  background: var(--purple); margin-top: 7px; flex-shrink: 0;
   234→}
   235→.demo-day-feature-content h4 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
   236→.demo-day-feature-content p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.5; }
   237→
   238→/* CTA */
   239→.cta-section {
   240→  padding: 160px 0; text-align: center; position: relative;
   241→  background: var(--cream);
   242→}
   243→.cta-section::before {
   244→  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
   245→  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
   246→  width: 500px; height: 500px;
   247→  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,79,204,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
   248→  pointer-events: none;
   249→}
   250→.cta-section h2 {
   251→  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 60px); font-weight: 700;
   252→  letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.1;
   253→}
   254→.cta-section p { font-size: 18px; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 40px; font-weight: 300; }
   255→
   256→/* FOOTER */
   257→footer { background: #1c1b1a; color: #f5f2eb; padding: 60px 0 40px; }
   258→.footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
   259→.footer-brand p { color: #8a8780; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 12px; max-width: 280px; line-height: 1.6; }
   260→.footer-col h4 { font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: #8a8780; margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: var(--font-display); }
   261→.footer-col a { display: block; font-size: 14px; color: #c4c1b8; padding: 4px 0; transition: color 0.2s; }
   262→.footer-col a:hover { color: #f5f2eb; }
   263→.footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,242,235,0.08); padding-top: 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: #8a8780; font-size: 13px; }
   264→
   265→/* RESPONSIVE */
   266→@media (max-width: 768px) {
   267→  section { padding: 80px 0; }
   268→  .hero { min-height: auto; padding-top: 120px; padding-bottom: 60px; }
   269→  .hero h1 { font-size: 40px; letter-spacing: -1px; }
   270→  .nav-links { display: none; }
   271→  .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
   272→  .intro-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
   273→  .demo-day-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
   274→  .hero-meta { gap: 20px; }
   275→}
   276→
   277→/* ANIMATIONS */
   278→.fade-up { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
   279→.fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
   280→</style>
   281→</head>
   282→<body>
   283→
   284→<nav>
   285→  <div class="container">
   286→    <a href="index.html" class="logo"><span>[</span>Habitat<span>]</span></a>
   287→    <ul class="nav-links">
   288→      <li><a href="https://luma.com/habitat" target="_blank">Events</a></li>
   289→      <li><a href="hackathon.html">Hackathons</a></li>
   290→      <li><a href="residency.html" class="active">Residency</a></li>
   291→      <li><a href="index.html#why">Why Habitat</a></li>
   292→      <li><a href="contact.html" class="nav-cta">Join waitlist &rarr;</a></li>
   293→    </ul>
   294→  </div>
   295→</nav>
   296→
   297→<!-- HERO -->
   298→<section class="hero">
   299→  <div class="container">
   300→    <div class="coming-badge">Coming 2026</div>
   301→    <div class="hero-label">Habitat Residency</div>
   302→    <h1>Live and build with<br><em>4 other founders</em><br>for 7 days.</h1>
   303→    <p class="hero-sub">You've already shipped an MVP. Now it's time to go deeper. Full immersion, dedicated mentorship, and a demo day in front of investors.</p>
   304→    <div class="hero-meta">
   305→      <div class="hero-meta-item">
   306→        <span class="hero-meta-label">Duration</span>
   307→        <span class="hero-meta-value">7 days</span>
   308→      </div>
   309→      <div class="hero-meta-item">
   310→        <span class="hero-meta-label">Cohort size</span>
   311→        <span class="hero-meta-value">5 founders</span>
   312→      </div>
   313→      <div class="hero-meta-item">
   314→        <span class="hero-meta-label">Format</span>
   315→        <span class="hero-meta-value">Live-in</span>
   316→      </div>
   317→      <div class="hero-meta-item">
   318→        <span class="hero-meta-label">Ends with</span>
   319→        <span class="hero-meta-value">Demo day</span>
   320→      </div>
   321→    </div>
   322→    <div class="hero-buttons">
   323→      <a href="contact.html?program=residency" class="btn-primary">Join the waitlist &rarr;</a>
   324→      <a href="#what" class="btn-secondary">How it works</a>
   325→    </div>
   326→  </div>
   327→</section>
   328→
   329→<!-- WHAT IS IT -->
   330→<section id="what">
   331→  <div class="container">
   332→    <div class="section-label fade-up">What it is</div>
   333→    <h2 class="section-title fade-up">From MVP to<br>business in a week.</h2>
   334→    <p class="section-sub fade-up">Habitat Residency is not a course. Not a coworking space. Not another accelerator. It's one week where you only build.</p>
   335→
   336→    <div class="intro-grid fade-up">
   337→      <div class="intro-text">
   338→        <h3>The premise is simple.</h3>
   339→        <p>Five founders, already past idea stage, live and work together for seven consecutive days. No commute. No context-switching. No meetings except the ones that matter.</p>
   340→        <p>You get a dedicated mentor — a practitioner, not a professor — who works alongside you for the full week. You get access to a VC network for feedback and potential funding. And on day seven, you pitch.</p>
   341→        <p>The goal isn't to raise money that week (though it happens). The goal is to leave knowing exactly where you're going and why.</p>
   342→      </div>
   343→      <div class="intro-stats">
   344→        <div class="intro-stat">
   345→          <div class="intro-stat-num">5</div>
   346→          <div class="intro-stat-label">founders per cohort — small enough to build real trust</div>
   347→        </div>
   348→        <div class="intro-stat">
   349→          <div class="intro-stat-num">7</div>
   350→          <div class="intro-stat-label">consecutive days of focused, undistracted building</div>
   351→        </div>
   352→        <div class="intro-stat">
   353→          <div class="intro-stat-num">1</div>
   354→          <div class="intro-stat-label">dedicated mentor with you the entire week</div>
   355→        </div>
   356→        <div class="intro-stat">
   357→          <div class="intro-stat-num">0</div>
   358→          <div class="intro-stat-label">equity taken — ever</div>
   359→        </div>
   360→      </div>
   361→    </div>
   362→  </div>
   363→</section>
   364→
   365→<!-- THE WEEK -->
   366→<section class="week-section">
   367→  <div class="container">
   368→    <div class="section-label fade-up">The week</div>
   369→    <h2 class="section-title fade-up">Seven days, structured to ship.</h2>
   370→    <p class="section-sub fade-up">Each day has a clear theme. You're building the whole time — but we make sure you're building the right things in the right order.</p>
   371→
   372→    <div class="week-grid">
   373→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   374→        <div class="day-label">Day 1</div>
   375→        <h3>Arrivals + alignment</h3>
   376→        <p>Move in, meet your cohort, set your week goal. What does success look like by Friday? Get brutally honest about where you are.</p>
   377→      </div>
   378→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   379→        <div class="day-label">Day 2</div>
   380→        <h3>Customer conversations</h3>
   381→        <p>Your first full day is not building. It's talking to users. Structured interviews, real insights, kill your assumptions early.</p>
   382→      </div>
   383→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   384→        <div class="day-label">Day 3 — 4</div>
   385→        <h3>Deep build</h3>
   386→        <p>Two full days of heads-down work. Morning standups with your mentor. Afternoon unblocking sessions. Evening reviews with the cohort.</p>
   387→      </div>
   388→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   389→        <div class="day-label">Day 5</div>
   390→        <h3>Test &amp; iterate</h3>
   391→        <p>Get real users on your product. Run experiments. Fix what's broken. Stop adding features. Make what you have work better.</p>
   392→      </div>
   393→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   394→        <div class="day-label">Day 6</div>
   395→        <h3>Story + pitch prep</h3>
   396→        <p>What's your narrative? Why this, why now, why you? Practice your demo until the story is effortless.</p>
   397→      </div>
   398→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   399→        <div class="day-label">Day 7</div>
   400→        <h3>Demo Day</h3>
   401→        <p>Investors, mentors, and the broader Habitat community. 10-minute demo + Q&A. The beginning of the next chapter.</p>
   402→      </div>
   403→    </div>
   404→  </div>
   405→</section>
   406→
   407→<!-- MENTORSHIP -->
   408→<section>
   409→  <div class="container">
   410→    <div class="section-label fade-up">Support structure</div>
   411→    <h2 class="section-title fade-up">Not advice. Presence.</h2>
   412→    <p class="section-sub fade-up">The difference between a good program and a transformative one is whether the people helping you are actually in the room.</p>
   413→
   414→    <div class="mentorship-grid">
   415→      <div class="mentorship-card fade-up">
   416→        <h3>Dedicated mentor</h3>
   417→        <p>One practitioner — a founder, operator, or investor who has done what you're trying to do — works with your cohort the full week. Not for 2 hours. For the week.</p>
   418→      </div>
   419→      <div class="mentorship-card fade-up">
   420→        <h3>VC office hours</h3>
   421→        <p>Investors from our network drop in for sessions throughout the week. Not to evaluate you — to help you think clearer. Evaluation happens at Demo Day, not before.</p>
   422→      </div>
   423→      <div class="mentorship-card fade-up">
   424→        <h3>Peer cohort</h3>
   425→        <p>Four other founders at the same stage, with complementary skills, working alongside you. The cohort is small enough to build genuine trust — and honest enough to tell you hard truths.</p>
   426→      </div>
   427→    </div>
   428→  </div>
   429→</section>
   430→
   431→<!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
   432→<section style="background: var(--cream);">
   433→  <div class="container">
