   447→        <div class="output-accent" style="background:var(--purple)"></div>
   448→        <h3>Your co-founder, maybe</h3>
   449→        <p>Teams form on the day. Some of the best founder partnerships start at events like this. You won't know until you build together.</p>
   450→      </div>
   451→    </div>
   452→  </div>
   453→</section>
   454→
   455→<!-- CTA -->
   456→<section class="cta-section">
   457→  <div class="container">
   458→    <h2 class="fade-up">Ready to build?</h2>
   459→    <p class="fade-up">Register your interest and we'll notify you when the next technical hackathon opens.</p>
   460→    <div class="hero-buttons fade-up" style="justify-content:center">
